    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab> Sancto ac venerabile <rs key="#Monasteries">cenobio</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Abbots #Monks #Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/47"
                            >sanctorum apostolorum et Christi confessoris Silvestri</orgName> sito
                        in <rs key="#Castle">castro</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Castle #Monasteries" ref="#places/15"
                        >Nonantule</placeName>, | <rs key="#City_territory">territorii</rs>
                        <placeName key="#City_territory" ref="#places/38">Motinensis</placeName>,
                        ubi domno <persName key="#Abbots" ref="#people/1242">Theodericus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbas</rs> preesse videtur, ideoque me Flavius Augustus
                            <persName key="#Emperor/king" ref="#people/32">Karo|lus</persName> a Deo
                        coronatus pacifico <rs key="#Emperor/king">rege</rs> quem ad lemosenam et
                        sanctam religiositatem in perpetuis valeturam. | Dans donom, transcrivo seo
                        emancipo in ad de iura dominioque ipsius cenovio fidelium ve|neratione
                        religia propter Dei caritatem et amoris ipso domno Teodericus abbas et
                        dictorum <rs key="#Monks">monachorum</rs> | deservientes veneratione, id est
                        monasterium <orgName
                            key="#Vici #Oil #Exotic_coins #Cereals #Decima #Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Wine #Rivers #Cells/hermitages #Curtes #Villas #Churches #Forests #Monasteries"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1131">Sancta Maria</orgName>, qui est fundeada
                        in <placeName>Fabrega</placeName>, cum omnia ad sibi pertine[ntia] et
                        adiacentia sua seo appendiciis suis, <rs key="#Vici">vicos</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Churches">ecclesias</rs>, <rs key="#Forests">selvas</rs> et montes
                        et planicia | reiacentes in <rs key="#Comitatus">cometatu</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Vici #Churches #Forests #Comitatus" ref="#places/2752"
                                ><geogName key="#Vici #Churches #Forests #Comitatus"
                                ref="#estates/1409">Perosianense</geogName></placeName> seo in
                        cometatu <geogName key="#Vici #Churches #Forests #Comitatus"
                            ref="#estates/1157"><placeName key="#Vici #Churches #Forests #Comitatus"
                                ref="#places/3662">Noceriense</placeName></geogName> seo in cometatu
                            <placeName ref="#places/1817" key="#Vici #Churches #Forests #Comitatus"
                                ><geogName key="#Vici #Churches #Forests #Comitatus"
                                ref="#estates/1158">Gobionense</geogName></placeName> atque | in
                        cometatu <placeName key="#Vici #Churches #Forests #Comitatus"
                            ref="#places/249"><geogName key="#Vici #Churches #Forests #Comitatus"
                                ref="#estates/1159">Assisense</geogName></placeName> vel per alias
                        cometatoras ad de ipso monasterio pertinente una cum <rs key="#Villas"
                            >villas</rs>, <rs key="#Curtes">cor|tes</rs>, corticellas, ecclesias et
                            <rs key="#Cells/hermitages">cellis</rs> ad sibi pertinentibus, una cum
                        selvas et <rs key="#Oil">oliveda</rs>, <rs key="#Rivers">fluviis</rs> et |
                        collibus, cum omnia adiacentia seu | pertinentia sua et cum sub sibi et
                        infra sibi habet in integrum, quod est inter terra <rs key="#Cereals"
                            >aradoricia</rs> |et terra <rs key="#Wine">vidata</rs> seo olivada, <rs
                            key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie">massaricii</rs> duo milia et si amplius
                        | fuerit quod ad ipsius monasterii pertinet de ipsio rebus, in cartula
                        nostra permanat et nemini subeat episcopo nisi tantum ecclesiam Romanam
                        triumphantem neque pro <rs key="#Decima">decimarum</rs> frugus, que sit ad
                        mona|chorum stipendia. Et si qui de hominibus qui precepta nostra violaverit
                        vel neglexerit, subeat pe|nam auri optimi <rs key="#Exotic_coins"
                            >mancosos</rs> .CCC. et insuper ad exilio dampnabitur et nostra precepta
                        | firma et inconvulsa permanat ad omnia. <persName key="#Count"><name
                                ref="Warnerius">Bernereus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Count">comes</rs>, <persName><name ref="Artusius"
                            >Artois</name></persName> de comes, <persName key="#Missus_regis #Count"
                                ><name ref="Warnefredus">Warne|fre</name></persName> comes <rs
                            key="#Missus_regis">missos</rs> domni Karoli interfuere. Ego <persName
                            key="#Notary #Writer #Scabini"><name ref="Guarnibertus"
                                >Guarnipret</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> et <rs key="#Scabini">scavino</rs> huius
                        pagine <rs key="#Writer">scriptor</rs> complivi. | (S.N.) Ego
                                <persName><name ref="Dominicus">Dominicus</name></persName>. (S.N.)
                        Ego <persName><name ref="Centius">Cincius</name></persName>. (S.N.) Ego
                                <persName><name ref="Wilielmus">Guillelmus</name></persName>. (S.N.)
                        Ego <persName key="#Notary"><name ref="Iacobus Gerardi">Iacobi
                                Gerardi</name></persName> imperiali auctoritate notarius hoc
                        exemplum ex quodam registro | monasteri Nonantule in quo registro subscripta
                        sunt nomina quorumdam dominorum cardinalium | in hunc modum. ...</ab>
                </div>
